{"tid":1790122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜「超美複製」迪士尼公主！復古靚照曝光　網友：戀愛了","createTime":"2019-12-19T18:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T17:02:46.000Z","uid":44730,"like":74,"dislike":393,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"b836ef0e245457e12151e716a67da7e851ad4f1c","tid":1790122,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"（18）日公布新照片，每位成員都以復古典雅裝扮出場，照片一出立刻引起熱烈討論，尤其是子瑜，一身黃色古典洋裝，模樣就像迪士尼《美女與野獸》的貝兒，美度破表。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/12/19/phpgTbjo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F12%2F19%2FphpgTbjo3.jpg&h=9129a787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/12/19/phpBh7Brg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F12%2F19%2FphpBh7Brg.jpg&h=f7db4ebc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"889f1fb40e3abf15b7816bcd022664749b9cdec8","tid":1790122,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":64,"score":-58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:01:23.000Z","msg":"「FANMEETING GOODS Making」的照片，9人都穿上復古典雅的洋裝，每人都美得像陶瓷娃娃，像是Rapper多賢，一身淡粉紅色洋裝，裙襬澎澎，金黃色的捲髮還戴著粉色髮箍，宛如櫥窗內的芭比娃娃，其他成員也不遑多讓，完美駕馭大紅色的洋裝，讓人看得目不轉睛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/19/2312340-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F19%2F2312340-PH.jpg&h=4f47a408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲9人9色，古典扮相引發熱烈討論。"},{"pid":"3e5640ef96d83e7f0ff80435b4218d8d8d99e46a","tid":1790122,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":44,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:01:41.000Z","msg":"不過令人注意的還有子瑜，一身亮黃色洋裝，頭髮用大黑色蝴蝶結綁起包頭，如花圈般的耳環，小細節也看得出造型師的用心。子瑜的扮相不但像一位復古名伶，更讓人不禁聯想到迪士尼動畫中，《美女與野獸》的女主角貝兒公主。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/12/19/php5QBY8i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F12%2F19%2Fphp5QBY8i.jpg&h=b7d127f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲不少網友認為，子瑜像極了迪士尼公主。"},{"pid":"0b55f06c20e780208b94f89678b927b60d4424b6","tid":1790122,"uid":44730,"like":11,"dislike":41,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/19/2312338-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F19%2F2312338-PH.jpg&h=811cacc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片一出，許多網友對子瑜的美貌相當驚艷，紛紛表示，「子瑜真是太有魅力了」、「子瑜太可愛了」、「她讓我想到貝兒公主」、「貝兒最美的版本」、「這個顏值等級太高了」、「我的公主」、「tzuyu So lovely」、「我美麗的子瑜」、「我的天啊」、「我想在夢裡見到子瑜」。"},{"pid":"ae944a89b541d39bab9c5597463e5e2bd5c28b3d","tid":1790122,"uid":555,"like":14,"dislike":45,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:01:58.000Z","msg":"魚仔仲靚過原版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32bf2f1682b2636f33d4b6e81a76a3762b04e60","tid":1790122,"uid":245552,"like":19,"dislike":28,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:02:34.000Z","msg":"對眼太細"},{"pid":"f489252515cca7bbdeeb44ddc0915ce4844f17c9","tid":1790122,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0793f7366b2e768b8c26659326a5538c0f80fb","tid":1790122,"uid":296191,"like":14,"dislike":37,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:17:50.000Z","msg":"靚到癲咗"},{"pid":"2fed24937174aabf81849f2fd0d581c67dcd7e51","tid":1790122,"uid":68678,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy"